      <hedline>
        <hl1>What to Do When the Baby Cries All Night</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>As a parent of a severely colicky baby, I found very little that was of help. I finally discovered a large dose of chocolate or, in an extreme case, Scotch did the trick. What to give the baby, however, remains a mystery to me.</p>
        <p>Peter Ryan  Vancouver, British Columbia  Nov. 11, 2005</p>
      </block>
